{"tid":2367121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反黑警疑炮製假掃賭 邀黑幫入警署商討安排細節 四警串謀妨礙司法公正今受審","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T10:02:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa1883d30cd752c9d8ffaa6cce01d3d0b61d8e9","tid":2367121,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科（O記）2018年派卧底調查荃灣黑幫，揭發有反黑警員疑為爭取「戰績」而設局造假，在工廈單位內安排假賭客、賭款及釣魚機，策劃一場「掃蕩行動」。涉案四名反黑組男警今否認串謀妨礙司法公正罪受審。控方指控四人在警員記事冊內造假，其中有人自稱「反黑南哥」，指示臥底警到警署商討「大龍鳳」；有人則吩咐臥底在賭場外的閉路電視加裝硬碟，稱「整返個hard disk上去先似樣」。<br />\n<br />\n案件今在區域法院開審，四名警員包括趙廣林（54歲）、賴福康（48歲）、傅裕文（36歲）、張子健（28歲），被控一項串謀妨礙司法公正罪，指他們於2018年5月2日至7月10日期間串謀陳少寶（39歲），連同王偉軍及「Eddy」犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/KVLDPTXEYND6XF5YXKKUJNC5T4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FKVLDPTXEYND6XF5YXKKUJNC5T4%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=466f79c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FKVLDPTXEYND6XF5YXKKUJNC5T4%2F&h=0bb8db29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/KVLDPTXEYND6XF5YXKKUJNC5T4/</a>"},{"pid":"94d705ea56a90df448f0546c49b81251fee8c678","tid":2367121,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02152e599121240bd53e3bd9e55a0e4d45b7de33","tid":2367121,"uid":174013,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-